  "title": "initialUiState doesn't work with routing",
  "body": "**Describe the bug 🐛**\r\ninitialUiState setting doesn't work if there is routing setting (not the simple \"routing: true\" but with seo-friendly urls settings).\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce 🔍**\r\nAs you can see from the live demo initialUiState query = 'stick' is not  working, if you comment line 31 \"routing: searchRouting,\" initialUiState will works.\r\nLive demo: https://codesandbox.io/s/flamboyant-cache-l6ne6?file=/src/app.js\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior 💭**\r\ninitialUiState works with routing enabled\r\n\r\n**Environment:**\r\n - OS: mac\r\n - Browser chrome\r\n - Version 81\r\n",
